{"tid":2426570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK的團魂！Jennie＆Lisa為正在拍攝《雪滴花》的Jisoo送上咖啡車、零食車！","createTime":"2021-02-28T07:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T11:23:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8d52c249bc7a07724b30a426409a05cd5e6077","tid":2426570,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_4b92e362146db6e26a6289b72a8f3b39/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-28/133952-898376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_4b92e362146db6e26a6289b72a8f3b39%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-28%2F133952-898376.jpg&h=c3608825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次是ROS&Eacute;！這次換Jennie＆Lisa，成員們感情真的很好啊&hearts;<br />\n<br />\n27日，BLACKPINK Jisoo在IG上傳一段影片上並寫下：「我人生裡首次兩個咖啡車&amp;零食車的主人公們Jennie、Lisa，首個咖啡車主人公ROS&Eacute;，我們BP最棒，我非常非常愛你們。」<br />\n<br />\nJennie送的咖啡車橫幅寫著：「我們漂亮的JICHO拜託大家了！JENDEUK&hearts;CHICHOO」；Lisa送的零食車橫幅寫著（用了三行詩）：「心動，下凡了，燦爛的英初 請美味的吃吧」。Jisoo也和車子合照，並發文感謝她們，成員們的感情真的很好啊～<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0799dc03990f24304a8969ee8f6cf311/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-28/133952-898366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0799dc03990f24304a8969ee8f6cf311%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-28%2F133952-898366.jpg&h=a1b09f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3022fd71592ee8d808b267218742fbfc/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-28/133952-898367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3022fd71592ee8d808b267218742fbfc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-28%2F133952-898367.jpg&h=c556da9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8b622670be559164bfd1b7a0ae1ab9ea/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-28/133952-898368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8b622670be559164bfd1b7a0ae1ab9ea%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-28%2F133952-898368.jpg&h=9c42c64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖：IG@sooyaaa__）<br />\n<br />\nJTBC新劇《雪滴花》以1987年首爾爲背景展開，講述某一天突然渾身是血地闖入女宿舍的名門大學生「秀浩」與在監視危機中將他隱藏並治療的女大學生之間，逆時代的愛情故事。由丁海寅、BLACKPINK Jisoo、張勝祖、尹世雅、金惠奫、鄭釉珍出演，預計在6月播出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5578aea268a18223333fb50908c867b8/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-28/133952-898369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5578aea268a18223333fb50908c867b8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-28%2F133952-898369.jpg&h=6c3bf8a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5041ed2f71335bc679330b2603707d7ba72a8478","tid":2426570,"uid":26183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"阿秀世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1db4da471717d7b20fee2a81da942d0ba4ca44","tid":2426570,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"好悶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主我"},{"pid":"b873466212fd538f338098ff6f0510e9bfddb9b5","tid":2426570,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5041ed2f71335bc679330b2603707d7ba72a8478","tid":2426570,"uid":26183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"阿秀世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"有無kiss戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2d03bf6545713beecfa56071eca515049a4fee","tid":2426570,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1db4da471717d7b20fee2a81da942d0ba4ca44","tid":2426570,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"好悶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-2